.Dd $Mdocdate$
.Dt LIBCERT 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm cert_config_set_ee ,
.Nm cert_config_set_ca ,
.Nm cert_config_set_ta
.Nd certificate type
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In cert.h
.Ft void
.Fn cert_config_set_ee "struct cert_config *config"
.Ft void
.Fn cert_config_set_ca "struct cert_config *config"
.Ft void
.Fn cert_config_set_ta "struct cert_config *config"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Fn cert_config_set_ee
functions sets the certificate type to
.Dq End Entity .
.Pp
The
.Fn cert_config_set_ca
functions sets the certificate type to
.Dq Certificate Authority .
.Pp
The
.Fn cert_config_set_ta
functions sets the certificate type to
.Dq Trust Anchor .
